name: PYRA - 001 (Evilmon)
description:
PYRA is summoned from merging an EVIL coin with a squirrel. The process may sound hurtful but the squirrel gets caught in an infinite orgasm loop when touched by an EVIL coin.

PYRA can be seen around olympic flames and campfires. Her flames only burn for a split second.

PYRA has been airsummoned to every wallet that owns 1 or more EVIL coin.


PYRA can evolve.
